{"tid":1083670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正義聯盟黨擲百萬拍《血傘》　描寫傘運推翻政府十年後的香港　蔡克健：年輕人不願撐政府拒參演","createTime":"2019-03-29T19:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T07:39:55.000Z","uid":215755,"like":13,"dislike":403,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"c95778e6e59305e8449ff08799424b8a6f5c6352","tid":1083670,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T19:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/600-0512-blood2-01_LihJo_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F600-0512-blood2-01_LihJo_1200x0.png&h=39f27478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正義聯盟黨宣佈，投資開拍電影《血傘》，故事講述佔領行動推翻現屆政府後，香港十年後的情境，預計製作投資最少100萬港元，由該黨副主席蔡克健編劇、執導，黨員及友好均將「粉墨登場」；《壹週刊》引述蔡克健表示，目前物色演員上遇到困難，不少年輕人得悉電影主題為撐政府，就拒絕參與拍攝，呼籲年輕人幫忙。電影預計7月開鏡，9月上映。<br />\n<br />\n正義聯盟黨今日就拍攝計劃舉行記者會，早前被指欺騙黨員金錢，遭罷免黨主席一職的李偲嫣並無現身。愛港之聲召集人高達斌及保衞香港運動發起人傅振中等人均有出席記者會，但未知是否將「粉墨登場」的友好之一。<br />\n<br />\n蔡克健表示，電影將由他與大陸友人開設的電影公司製作。他指自己在佔領期間已在構思，如果「雨傘革命」成功推翻特區政府，香港將會被一班「披上『民主』的暴徒」管治，希望透過電影讓港人反思，香港應走安穩繁榮之路，還是如伊拉克、敘利亞等地一樣，令人民為逃避戰禍而流離失所。<br />\n<br />\n正義聯盟黨另宣佈由本月22日起，連續18個星期日在全港擺街站，收集市民簽名要求重新推出「一簽多行」；蔡克健認為，重推一簽多行，會令香港因過往激進團體衝擊陸客而變得負面的形象，有所改善，以助本港經濟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/13232931_1097913923605936_189416580450753199_n_AbR4O_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F13232931_1097913923605936_189416580450753199_n_AbR4O_1200x0.jpg&h=4acef6e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa1b5f67ceec2c69b79a7fb9c9b14eb110433e4c","tid":1083670,"uid":52459,"like":318,"dislike":0,"score":318,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T19:12:56.000Z","msg":"得個一球可以拍到乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3cbb5d9dbaf90813354c52339ad3d48f4873d0e","tid":1083670,"uid":48582,"like":210,"dislike":0,"score":210,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T19:14:30.000Z","msg":"講咗幾年<br />\n但仲未交到貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509a494072b0be4ea7daae4fe45d8e0dcc7b8064","tid":1083670,"uid":54256,"like":225,"dislike":0,"score":225,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T19:14:50.000Z","msg":"講左咁耐都未拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雨革之後我大學我都就黎讀完啦屌"},{"pid":"b92305600f9191a5f9d9a8092a32ba90777e755d","tid":1083670,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":44,"score":-44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T19:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/13232931_1097913923605936_189416580450753199_n_AbR4O_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F13232931_1097913923605936_189416580450753199_n_AbR4O_1200x0.jpg&h=4acef6e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抽到乾哂"},{"pid":"548df5fa6c7e83a18fb5a6d6d8dbbd2a86ceda4d","tid":1083670,"uid":28181,"like":62,"dislike":2,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T19:38:08.000Z","msg":"Cap左水就走啦仲拍鬼拍馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3197c497198b1917ce1a1fd0216b88019346859a","tid":1083670,"uid":28181,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"548df5fa6c7e83a18fb5a6d6d8dbbd2a86ceda4d","tid":1083670,"uid":28181,"like":62,"dislike":2,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T19:38:08.000Z","msg":"Cap左水就走啦仲拍鬼拍馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T19:40:02.000Z","msg":"我就唔信搵唔到人拍，昆明擺檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4dca986fea71f2becc9c0f45f0ba055c713b0f","tid":1083670,"uid":